overview: Whether it's a new college, your first job, or even losing your virginity, your first time is always a daunting time. So imagine losing your virginity on any of those first days. These young lads are taking big steps out in the big wide world and either grabbing life by the balls or falling straight to their knees! Will these lads end the day with a palm full of cash or a face full of spunk? There is only one way to find out.
title: First Time Teens
